/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-14-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-14-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-14.jpg 2000w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade 2024 review\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade 2024 review\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-10.jpg\" alt=\"Pivot Switchblade 2024 review\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-10.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-10-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-10-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-10-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-10-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade 2024 review\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade 2024 review\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>By the last few long descents of the day, I was feeling more confident on the newest Switchblade than any of the previous generations. Despite being stiff in all the right places with razor-sharp handling, the newest Switchblade is a bike that seems to be incredibly user-friendly. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>At this point, I’ve ridden all of the past Switchblades, and there is no question that this is the best yet. Fans of internal storage will be disappointed, but the Pivot Dock System does give you an additional spot to stash your tools. On the plus side, the frame will fit a large water bottle easily, and without a special cage. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-12.jpg\" alt=\"Pivot Switchblade 2024 review\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-12.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-12-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-12-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-12-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-12-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-12-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade 2024 review\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade 2024 review\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ultimately, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pivot-switchblade-2024-improved-suspension-updated-geometry/\" target=\"_blank\">the new Switchblade</a> isn’t a huge departure from the version released in 2020, but it has the right updates to keep it competitive. It might not be enough of a change to tempt current Switchblade owners to upgrade, but those who do are surely getting a better bike. </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pivot-switchblade-review-2024/\">Pivot Switchblade Review: A Great Bike Gets Even Better</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b1c93af9f05e7e4bdddb9f81955fd634208c733d355102d4cca4598cc668c890","category":"Cycling"}